name: Jangra Chemicals
overview: Incepted in the year 2007, at Jalandhar (Punjab, India ), we, “Jangra Chemicals”, established ourselves as the alleged manufacturer and supplier of an extreme quality gamut of Car Care Products, Household cleaners and Wavex Products. Our wide range of products comprises Multi-purpose Cleaner, Tyre Polsih, Car Shampoo, Tile Stain Remover, Hand Wash Liquid etc. that are formulated by our adroit professionals as per the requirements of our customer. The offered range of cleaners, polishes etc. are prepared at our state-of-the-art processing labs using high grade chemical compounds and cutting edge technology. We assure our clients that the chemicals use in the formulation of our provided range is sourced from the trusted and reliable vendors of the industry. Also, the procured factor inputs are vigilantly examined on varied quality aspects to avoid any kind of discrepancy in our offered products. These products are extensively valued for their features such as effectiveness, UV protection, safe used, rich lather, pleasing fragrance
